@startuml
title GoF Pattern : Observer + Memento

note as GoFLabel
  **<<Observer + Memento>>**
end note

class Document {
  + id: Integer
  + content: String
  + createMemento(): Memento
  + restore(Memento m): void
  + attach(o: Observer): void
  + detach(o: Observer): void
  + notify(): void
}
class Toolbar {
  # toolbarItems: List<ToolbarItem>
  # update(Document d): void
  # addToolbarItem(ToolbarItem ti): void
}
class StatusBar {
  # statusBarItems: List<StatusBarItem>
  # update(Document d): void
  # addStatusBarItem(StatusBarItem si): void
}
class PreviewPanel {
  + previewContent: String
  + update(Document d): void
  + refresh(): void
}
interface Memento {
  # restore(Document d): void
}

Document --> Toolbar
Document --> StatusBar
Document --> PreviewPanel
Toolbar *--> Document
StatusBar *--> Document
GoFLabel .. Document
@enduml